{[%mdl 36865] Purdy's best correspondence game, according to Purdy.} 1. c4 {Myers Harding Purdy} Nf6 2. d4 e6 3. Nc3 (3. Nf3 {Myers: This game was probably the model for Purdy's opening play.} d5 4. Nc3 Be7 5. Bg5 h6 6. Bh4 O-O 7. e3 Ne4 8. Bxe7 Qxe7 9. cxd5 Nxc3 10. bxc3 exd5 11. Qb3 Qd6 12. c4 dxc4 13. Bxc4 Nc6 14. Qc3 Bg4 15. Nd2 Rad8 16. O-O Ne7 17. Rfc1 b6 18. Ne4 Qd7 19. Ng3 c6 20. Qa3 Ra8 21. h3 Be6 22. Be2 Rac8 23. Nh5 Ng6 24. Qb2 f5 25. a4 f4 26. Bd3 Bf5 27. e4 Bxh3 28. f3 Qe7 29. a5 Nh4 30. axb6 axb6 31. gxh3 Qg5+ 32. Kh1 Qxh5 33. Be2 Kh8 34. Ra3 Rf6 35. Rg1 Nf5 36. Kh2 Ne3 37. Ra7 Rg6 38. Qa1 Rg5 39. d5 Qxh3+ {0-1 Guimard,C-Eliskases,E/Mar del Plata ARG 1941/}) 3... d5 4. Bg5 Be7 5. e3 O-O 6. Nf3 Ne4 7. Bxe7 Qxe7 8. cxd5 Nxc3 9. bxc3 exd5 10. Qb3 Qd6 (10... Rd8 $1 11. Bd3 c5 12. dxc5 (12. Qa3 b6 13. O-O Nc6 14. Bb5 c4 15. Qxe7 Nxe7 16. Ba4 Bf5 17. Rfc1 a6 18. Bc2 b5 19. Nd2 Be6 20. Rcb1 f5 21. a3 Ng6 22. f4 Rdb8 23. Nf3 Rb7 24. Ne5 Nxe5 25. fxe5 Rab8 26. Rb2 a5 27. Rab1 Kf7 28. Rf1 b4 29. axb4 axb4 30. g4 Kg8 31. gxf5 Bd7 32. e6 Bc6 33. cxb4 Rxb4 34. Rxb4 Rxb4 35. Ra1 Kf8 36. Ra6 Be8 37. e4 Rb5 38. Ra8 Ke7 39. Rxe8+ Kxe8 40. Ba4 {1-0 Marshall,F-Treybal,K/Folkestone ENG 1933/}) 12... Qxc5 13. O-O Nc6 14. Nd4 Ne5 15. Be2 b6 16. f4 Nc6 17. Rad1 Bb7 18. Rf3 Rac8 19. Rh3 Re8 20. Bg4 Rc7 21. Qc2 h6 22. Qf2 Nxd4 23. exd4 Qe7 24. Bf5 Ba6 25. Bb1 Qe2 26. Qxe2 Rxe2 27. a3 Rce7 28. Bf5 Ra2 29. Bg4 Rxa3 30. Rh5 Bc4 31. Bf3 Rxc3 32. Bxd5 g6 33. Re5 Rxe5 34. dxe5 Rd3 35. Rxd3 Bxd3 36. Kf2 Bf5 37. Bc4 a5 38. Ke3 Kf8 39. Kd4 Ke7 40. Be2 h5 41. Bb5 Bd7 {0-1 Mikenas,V-Book,E/Munich GER 1936/}) 11. c4 (11. Bd3 Nd7 12. O-O c6 13. c4 dxc4 14. Bxc4 Nb6 15. Bd3 Nd5 16. Rab1 b6 17. Rfc1 Bb7 18. e4 Nf4 19. Bf1 Rad8 20. g3 Ne6 21. Rd1 Qe7 22. Bg2 Nc7 23. Nh4 Qf6 24. Qb2 Rfe8 25. f4 Qe6 26. Nf5 f6 27. Ne3 h6 28. Rbc1 Rd7 29. Bf3 c5 30. d5 Qf7 31. f5 Na6 32. Ng2 Rd6 33. Nf4 Re5 34. Rd2 Qd7 35. Qb3 Bc8 36. g4 Re8 37. h4 Qe7 38. Ng6 Qf7 39. Rg2 Nc7 40. Nf4 Qe7 41. Ne6 Bxe6 42. fxe6 Red8 43. Rf1 Nxe6 44. dxe6 Qxe6 45. g5 Qxb3 46. axb3 hxg5 47. hxg5 Kf8 48. Be2 Re8 49. Rg4 Re5 50. Bc4 Ke8 51. gxf6 gxf6 52. Rg8+ Ke7 53. Rg7+ Kd8 54. Rxa7 Rxe4 55. Rf7 Rg4+ 56. Kh1 {½-½ Olexa,V-Ahman,H/corr ICCA 1949/}) 11... dxc4 12. Bxc4 Nc6 13. Qc3 (13. O-O Na5 14. Qc3 Nxc4 15. Qxc4 Be6 16. Qc2 Rac8 17. Rfc1 b6 18. Ng5 g6 19. Nxe6 Qxe6 20. Qc6 Qxc6 21. Rxc6 Rfd8 22. Rac1 Rd7 23. Kf1 Kf8 24. Ke2 Ke7 25. Kf3 Kd8 26. Kf4 Rd6 27. Kg5 Kd7 28. Rxd6+ cxd6 29. Rxc8 Kxc8 30. Kf6 d5 31. e4 Kd7 32. e5 Ke8 33. e6 fxe6 34. Kxe6 Kd8 35. f4 Kc7 36. g4 {1-0 Nielsen,H-Korning,P/Odense DEN 1945/}) (13. Be2 Be6 14. Qc3 Nb4 15. a3 Nd5 16. Qc2 Rac8 17. O-O c5 18. Qb2 cxd4 19. Qxd4 Qc5 20. Qh4 Bf5 21. Nd4 Bg6 22. Qg3 Rfe8 23. Bf3 b5 24. h3 a5 25. Nb3 Qc4 26. Nxa5 Qc3 27. Nb7 Re5 28. Nd6 Rb8 29. Rac1 Qb2 30. Bxd5 Rxd5 31. Nc8 Qe5 32. Ne7+ Qxe7 33. Qxb8+ Rd8 34. Rc8 {1-0 Stahlberg,G-Hounie Fleurquin,C/Mar del Plata ARG 1945/}) 13... Bg4 $1 (13... Qb4 14. Qxb4 Nxb4 15. Kd2 Nc6 16. Rhc1 Bg4 17. Ne1 Rfd8 18. Be2 Bxe2 19. Kxe2 Rd7 20. Rab1 Nd8 21. Nd3 c6 22. Ne5 Re7 23. Nd3 Ne6 24. Kd2 Rd8 25. Nc5 Nxc5 26. Rxc5 Kf8 {½-½ Germek,M-Tot,B/Zagreb YUG 1949/}) (13... b6 14. Rc1 Bb7 15. O-O Na5 16. Bd3 Bxf3 17. gxf3 c6 18. Qc2 g6 19. Rfd1 Rac8 20. Qe2 Rc7 21. Rc2 Rd8 22. Rdc1 Qe7 23. Be4 Rd6 24. Qe1 Qg5+ 25. Kh1 Qh5 26. f4 Re7 27. Qb4 c5 28. dxc5 Rd1+ 29. Rxd1 Qxd1+ 30. Kg2 Qg4+ 31. Kf1 Qd1+ {½-½ Skold,K-Stoltz,G/Marianske Lazne CSR 1951/}) 14. Nd2 (14. Be2 Rae8 15. O-O Bf5 16. Rfd1 Be4 17. Rac1 Re7 18. a3 Bd5 19. Ne5 Nxe5 20. dxe5 Qe6 21. Qc5 Bc6 22. Bb5 Bxb5 23. Qxb5 c6 24. Qc5 Qxe5 25. Qxa7 f5 26. Qd4 Qxd4 27. Rxd4 Ra8 28. Rc3 Kf7 29. g4 fxg4 30. Rxg4 Rd7 31. Rb4 Ra5 32. Rcb3 b5 33. Rc3 Rc7 34. Rd4 h6 35. Rd6 c5 36. Rd5 c4 37. Kg2 Ke6 38. e4 Rca7 39. f4 b4 40. f5+ Kf6 41. axb4 Ra2+ {½-½ Freise,H-Heilemann,M/Voelklingen BRD 1970/}) 14... Rad8 15. O-O Ne7 (15... Kh8 16. Rac1 Qg6 17. Rfe1 Bh3 18. Bf1 Be6 19. a3 f5 20. Rb1 Bd5 21. f3 Qf6 22. Rxb7 f4 23. e4 Nxd4 24. Rxc7 Bc6 25. e5 Qh4 26. Ne4 Bxe4 27. Rxe4 Ne6 28. Rc6 Rfe8 29. Rd6 Qe7 30. Qd2 h6 31. Bc4 Nc5 32. Rxf4 Rb8 33. Qd4 Rb1+ 34. Kf2 Rc8 35. Rf7 Qg5 36. h4 Nd3+ 37. Bxd3 Qd2+ 38. Kg3 Qe1+ 39. Kg4 {1-0 Nikolic,P-Miladinovic,I/Banja Vrucica BIH 2009/}) 16. Rfc1 b6 17. Ne4 Qd7 18. Ng3 (18. a4 $5) 18... c6 19. Qa3 Ra8 {Myers: Purdy points out that the game has followed Guimard-Eliskases, Mar del Plata 1941, to this point, except that Black had played one extra move, ...h7-h6.} (19... Nd5 $5) 20. Rc2 Be6 21. Bxe6 Qxe6 22. Rac1 Rfd8 23. Ne2 Rd7 (23... Qd6 24. Qa4 Rdc8 25. Qb3 Rc7 26. g3 Rac8 27. Nf4 h6 28. Nd3 Nd5 29. e4 $14 {Myers}) 24. h3 g6 (24... h6 $5 {Purdy} 25. Nf4 Qd6 26. Qb3 Rc7 27. a4 Rac8 28. a5 c5 29. dxc5 Rxc5 30. Rxc5 Rxc5 31. Rd1 Qc7 32. axb6 axb6 33. Nd3 $14 {Myers}) 25. Nf4 Qd6 26. Qb2 Rc8 27. Nd3 c5 $2 (27... Rdc7 $5 28. e4 c5 29. d5 Nc6 30. Nxc5 bxc5 31. dxc6 Rxc6 32. e5 Qe7 33. Rc4 $14 {Myers}) 28. Ne5 $1 Rdc7 29. dxc5 Qf6 30. Qd4 Nf5 31. Qf4 Qe6 32. Nd3 $1 bxc5 (32... Qd7 33. Rc3 Qd8 34. Qe5 Rd7 35. Nf4 Qc7 36. Qxc7 Rdxc7 37. g4 $16 {Myers}) 33. Rxc5 Rxc5 34. Rxc5 Rxc5 35. Nxc5 Qxa2 36. Qb8+ $1 Kg7 37. Nd7 Qa1+ 38. Kh2 Qa3 39. Qe5+ Kh6 40. Nc5 $1 Qb4 (40... f6 41. Qf4+ $1 Kg7 42. Qc7+ Kg8 43. e4 Ng7 44. Qd8+ Kf7 45. Qd5+ Kf8 46. Qd6+ Kf7 47. Qd7+ Kf8 48. Qd5 a6 49. Nd7+ Ke7 50. e5 fxe5 51. Nxe5 Qa4 52. Nc6+ Kf8 53. Qf3+ $18 {Myers}) 41. g4 f6 42. Qc7 Ng7 $2 (42... Qb6 $5 43. Qxb6 axb6 44. Nd7 Nd6 45. Nxb6 Kg5 46. Nd7 f5 47. f4+ Kh4 48. Ne5 fxg4 49. hxg4 h6 50. Kg2 Ne4 51. Kf3 Nd2+ 52. Kf2 Ne4+ 53. Kg2 g5 54. f5 h5 55. Kf3 Nd2+ 56. Ke2 Ne4 $11 {Myers}) 43. Qxa7 Qb2 44. Nd3 Qc3 45. Qd7 f5 (45... Qc2 46. h4 Qd1 47. Ne5 Qxd7 48. Nxd7 Ne8 49. Nxf6 Nxf6 50. g5+ $18 {Myers}) 46. Qd6 (46. g5+ $1 Kxg5 47. Qe7+ Kh6 48. Ne5 Qd2 $2 49. Nf7+ Kh5 50. Qg5# {Myers}) 46... Ne8 47. Qf8+ Ng7 48. gxf5 gxf5 49. Qd6+ (49. h4 $1 Qc6 50. Qe7 Qg6 51. Nf4 Qg4 52. Qf6+ $18 {Myers}) 1-0


