 $1 Qxc5 35. Rxf7 Qe5+ 36. Kg4 Qe6+ 37. Kxg5 Nf3+ 38. Rxf3 exf3 39. Qd4 Qe5+ 40. Qxe5 Rxe5+ $11 {Timm}) 34. Kf1 Nxh2+ 35. Ke1 Nf3+ 36. Kf1 Qh3+ 37. Ke2 Ne5 $1 38. Be3 (38. Rd6 Nxc4 39. Rdd7 {Timm} e3 $3 40. fxe3 Nxe3 41. Qg1 Nd5+ 42. Be7 Qe6+ $19 {Myers}) 38... g4 $1 39. Rb8 Qf3+ 40. Kf1 Raxb8 41. axb8=Q Qh3+ 42. Ke2 Rxb8 43. Rd8+ Rxd8 44. Qxd8+ Kh7 45. Qd4 Qf3+ 46. Kd2 Qf5 47. Kc3 Nd3 $19 {Myers}) (31... e3 $142 $6 {Napolitano} 32. fxe3 $1 hxg2 33. Rxf7 Qxc5 34. Rg7+ Kh8 35. Rh7+ Kg8 36. Rbg7+ $11 {Harding}) (31... Qxc5 $142 $6 32. Rxf7 (32. Qxh3 $2 e3 33. fxe3 Rxe3 $19 {Harding}) 32... Qe5 33. Rfd7 $1 Qa1+ (33... c5 34. Qd1 Kf8 35. Qd6+ Qxd6 36. Rxd6 Nxg2 $11 {Myers}) 34. Qd1 $8 Qxd1+ 35. Rxd1 {Harding} Nxg2 36. Rdd7 Ne1 37. Rg7+ Kh8 38. Rh7+ Kg8 39. Rxh3 Nf3+ 40. Kg2 Nh4+ 41. Kf1 Rf8 42. Ke2 Rad8 43. Rg3 Nf3 44. h4 Rd3 45. Rg4 Nd4+ $11 {Myers}) (31... Nxg2 $143 $4 32. Rxf7 Qxf7 (32... Qxc5 33. Rg7+ Kh8 34. Rh7+ Kg8 35. Rbg7+ $18 {Harding}) 33. Rxf7 Kxf7 34. Qxh3 Nh4 35. Qd7+ Kg6 36. Qxc6+ $18 {Myers}) 32. gxf3 exf3 33. Kf1 $1 (33. Be3 $2 $11 Rad8 34. Qd1 Qg4+ 35. Kf1 Qg2+ 36. Ke1 Rxe3+ {Napolitano thought this position was winning for Black.} 37. Kd2 Rxd7+ 38. Kxe3 $1 Rxd1 39. a8=Q+ Kg7 40. Qa7 $8 {Bogan} Kg6 41. Rxf7 Kh5 42. Rf8 (42. Rh7+ Kg4 43. Rh4+ gxh4 44. Qg7+ Kh5 45. Qh7+ Kg5 46. Qg7+ $11) 42... Re1+ 43. Kd2 Rd1+ 44. Kc2 Rc1+ 45. Kb2 Rb1+ 46. Ka2 Ra1+ 47. Kxa1 Qf1+ $11 {Myers}) (33. Be7 $2 $11 Qg4+ 34. Kf1 Qg2+ 35. Ke1 Qg1+ 36. Kd2 Qxf2+ 37. Kc1 Qe1+ 38. Kb2 f2 39. Qg3 Qe2+ 40. Kb3 f1=Q 41. Qxg5+ Kh7 42. Qh4+ Kg7 43. Qg5+ $11 {Myers}) 33... Qxc5 34. Qc3 $1 (34. Rxf7 $5 Qe5 35. Rg7+ Qxg7 {Purdy} 36. c5+ $1 Kh8 37. Rxg7 Kxg7 38. Qb7+ Kf8 39. Qh7 Red8 40. Ke1 $1 g4 41. Qf5+ Ke7 42. Qxg4 Rd5 43. Qg3 Ke6 44. Qxh3+ Ke5 45. Qg3+ Kd4 46. Qf4+ Kxc5 47. Qb8 $18 {Myers}) 34... Rf8 35. Qd3 Qe5 $8 36. Qxf3 Rae8 37. Rb1 $2 (37. Qxh3 $1 Qa1+ 38. Kg2 Re1 39. Qf5 Rg1+ 40. Kf3 (40. Kh3 Qf1#) 40... g4+ 41. Kf4 Qc1+ 42. Ke5 Re1+ 43. Kd6 Qa3+ 44. Kc7 Re6 45. Qxg4+ (45. a8=Q $2