Kc5 {0-1 Lacroix,S-Meng,F/Montreal 2002/}) 15. exd5 Qxd5 16. Ne4 (16. Qe2 Qe6 17. Nf1 Bxf3 18. Qxf3 Rad8 19. Ng3 Qd5 20. Ne4 Kh8 21. Bb3 Qd3 22. Re3 Qd7 23. Ng5 Kg8 24. Re1 h6 25. Ne4 Nxe4 26. Qxe4 Kh8 27. Bc2 f5 28. Qe2 Rf6 29. a4 Qb7 30. Qh5 f4 31. Be4 Bd6 32. axb5 axb5 33. b3 Qb6 34. Qf3 Bc7 35. Bc2 b4 36. Bb2 bxc3 37. Bxc3 Nd4 38. Bxd4 exd4 39. Ra8 Bb8 40. Re7 g6 41. Rb7 Qd6 42. Bd3 Re6 43. b4 Rc8 44. b5 Qd8 45. Ra1 Qf6 46. Qd5 Rd8 47. Qf3 Rde8 48. Ra6 Bd6 49. Bc4 Re1+ 50. Kh2 Rd8 51. Rf7 Qh4 52. Rxd6 {1-0 Pajukari,S-Molsa,Y/corr 1989/}) (16. Nf1 Bxf3 17. Qxf3 Qxf3 18. gxf3 Rad8 19. Be3 Nd5 20. a4 b4 21. c4 Nf4 22. Bxf4 exf4 23. Be4 Na5 24. Bxh7+ Kxh7 25. Rxe7 Nxc4 26. b3 Na5 27. Re4 Nxb3 28. Rb1 Nd4 29. Rxb4 Nxf3+ 30. Kg2 Nh4+ 31. Kg1 g5 32. Rb1 Rd3 33. Kh2 Kg7 34. Re7 Ng6 35. Reb7 Rh8 36. a5 Rdxh3+ 37. Kg1 Rh1+ 38. Kg2 R8h3 39. f3 Nh4+ 40. Kf2 Rxf3+ 41. Ke2 Rg1 {0-1 De Oliveira,J-Santo,R/corr CXEB 2001/}) 16... Qxd1 17. Nxf6+ (17. Bxd1 Nxe4 18. Rxe4 Rfd8 19. Re1 e4 20. Nd4 Nxd4 21. cxd4 Bg6 22. Bd2 Rxd4 23. Bc3 Rd7 24. Bc2 b4 25. Be5 f5 26. g4 Rf8 27. gxf5 Bxf5 28. Bxe4 Bxh3 29. Re3 Be6 30. Bc6 Rd2 31. Bg3 Rf6 32. Rae1 Kf7 33. Be8+ Kxe8 34. Rxe6 Rxe6 35. Rxe6 Kf7 36. Rxa6 Rxb2 37. Ra7 Ke6 38. Kg2 Bf6 39. Kf3 Kd5 40. Ra6 Kc4 41. Ra8 Kd3 42. Rb8 Bc3 43. Bd6 Kc2 44. Ra8 Kb1 45. a4 Ra2 46. a5 b3 47. Rc8 Bxa5 48. Bf4 Rc2 49. Ra8 Be1 50. Be3 b2 51. Ra7 Rc3 52. Ke2 Kc2 {0-1 Kattinger,I-Nicolau,A/Split 1963/}) 17... Bxf6 18. Bxd1 Bg6 19. Bg5 Bxg5 20. Nxg5 Rad8 21. Bf3 Na5 22. Rad1 Nc4 23. b3 Nd2 24. Bb7 h6 25. Nf3 Nxf3+ 26. Bxf3 f6 27. Bb7 a5 28. c4 bxc4 29. bxc4 Bf7 30. Rxd8 Rxd8 31. c5 Rd7 32. Bf3 Rc7 33. Rc1 Kf8 34. a3 Ke7 35. Kf1 f5 36. Ke1 e4 37. Be2 f4 38. Bb5 Bd5 39. Ke2 Ke6 40. Kd2 Ke5 41. g3 g5 42. a4 Kd4 43. c6 Ke5 44. gxf4+ gxf4 45. h4 Kd6 46. Rg1 Bxc6 47. Rg6+ Kc5 48. Rxh6 Rd7+ 49. Kc2 Bxb5 50. axb5 Kxb5 51. Re6 Rc7+ 52. Kb2 Rc4 53. Re5+ Kb4 54. h5 a4 55. h6 a3+ 56. Kb1 e3 57. fxe3 f3 58. h7 f2 59. Rf5 Kb3 60. Rxf2 Rh4 {½-½ Panchenko,A-Beliavsky,A/Sukhumi U20 1970/}) 14... Qxd5 15. Qe2 Rfe8 16. Ne4 {Harding: ''} Bh5 $6 (16... Qd7 17. Rd1 Qc8 18. Bg5 Nxe4 19. Qxe4 g6 20. Bxe7 Bf5 21. Qh4 Rxe7 22. Ng5 h5 23. Bb3 Raa7 24. h3 Be6 25. Nxe6 fxe6 26. Qf6 Kh7 27. Rd6 Rf7 28. Qxe6 Qxe6 29. Rxe6 Rac7 30. Rd1 b4 31. Rdd6 Ne7 32. cxb4 {1-0 Purdy,C-Fell,L/corr 1948/}) (16... Rac8 $5) 17. Rd1 (17. Nxf6+ $1 Bxf6 18. Be4 Qe6 19. a4 $1 $16 {Myers}) 17... Qe6 18. Ng3 Bg6 19. Bb3 $1 Qc8 20. Nh4 $1 Na5 21. Nxg6 hxg6 22. Bc2 Qc7 (22... Qe6 $5) 23. Ne4 Nxe4 24. Qxe4 Rad8 25. Re1 Nc4 26. Qe2 Bf6 (26... f5 $5) 27. Be4 (27. a4 $5) 27... Qd7 $2 (27... Be7 $5 {[%cal Gf7f5]}) 28. a4 $1 Re6 29. axb5 axb5 30. Ra8 (30. b3 Nd2 31. Bxd2 Qxd2 32. Qxd2 Rxd2 33. c4 bxc4 34. bxc4 Re8 35. c5 Be7 36. Rec1 Rc8 37. c6 f5 $14 {Myers}) 30... Rxa8 31. Bxa8 Rd6 32. Be4 (32. Bf3 $5) 32... Nd2 33. Bc2 Rd5 34. f3 (34. b3 $5 e4 35. c4 bxc4 36. bxc4 Rd4 37. c5 Qd5 38. Rd1 Nb3 39. Be3 Rxd1+ 40. Qxd1 Nd4 41. Qb1 $14 {Myers}) 34... Bg5 35. Kh1 Qd8 36. g3 $6 (36. b3 $5) 36... Bh6 37. Qf2 (37. Rd1 $5) 37... Kh7 38. Re2 Nc4 39. f4 exf4 40. gxf4 Ne5 $2 (40... Rh5 $5) 41. fxe5 Bxc1 42. e6 fxe6 43. Qf3 (43. Qf1 $5) 43... Qd7 44. Qh3+ Kg8 45. Rxe6 Rh5 46. Qg4 Qb7+ 47. Qe4 $1 (47. Qg2 $5 Qxg2+ 48. Kxg2 Bxb2 49. Bxg6 Rg5+ 50. Kf3 Ba3 51. Kf4 $14 {Myers}) 47... Qxe4+ 48. Bxe4 Kf7 49. Rb6 Ke7 50. Bxg6 Rh6 51. b3 (51. Rb7+ $5) 51... Bb2 $6 (51... Bf4 $1 $11 {Myers}) 52. Rb7+ Kf6 53. Bd3 Bxc3 54. Rb6+ (54. Rxb5 $1) 54... Ke7 55. Rxb5 Rd6 56. Bf1 Rd2 57. Rc5 Bd4 (57... Bf6 $5) 58. Rc4 (58. Rd5 $5) 58... Kd6 59. h3 {Harding: 'See notes in my Winning at CC book that were based on Purdy's own notes. Then the corrections later found, see Correspondence Chess 131 p25 and Byron Jacobs' book Analyse to Win p.80'} (59. b4 $5) 59... Ke5 60. Ra4 Kf4 61. b4 Be3 62. Ra3 Kf3 63. Bg2+ $4 {Harding: '?'} (63. Bc4 $1) 63... Kf2 $1 64. Ra1 $4 (64. Rxe3 $5 $19) 64... Kg3 65. Re1 Bd4 66. Rb1 Re2 (66... Rxg2 $1 {Harding: 'Would have been quickest way to win? Purdy thought an error because of'} 67. Rb3+